# ye page h jab koi code kisi page pe kam nal kare to wo page 404 error dikhata hai.ai jata hai. Iska matlab hai ki jo resource aap dhoondh rahe hain wo server pe nahi mil raha hai. Ye error tab hota hai jab URL galat ho, resource delete ho gaya ho, ya fir server pe koi issue ho. 404 error ko handle karne ke liye aap apne web application me custom 404 error page bana sakte hain jo users ko better experience de sake. Iske alawa, aap apne website ke links ko regularly check kar sakte hain taaki broken links na ho. Agar aap kisi website ka developer hain, to ensure karein ki sabhi resources sahi tarah se server pe host kiye hain aur URLs sahi hain. 404 error ko samajhna aur usse effectively handle karna web development ka ek important hissa hai.
